  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the effectiveness of the telephone intervention
      program for caregivers of colorectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      telephone Intervention refer to provide counseling and education to caregivers of colorectal
      cancer by mode of telephone
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
